If the plan of care includes a course of treatment for therapy services: 
 • The course of therapy treatment must be established by the physician or allowed 
practitioner after any needed consultation with the qualified therapist; 
 • The plan must include measurable therapy treatment goals which pertain directly 
to the patient’s illness or injury, and the patient’s resultant impairments; 
 • The plan must include the expected duration of therapy services; and
